Title: node collector PSP: add missing volumes and capabilities
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: helm
Date: 1650897164
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0-alpha.1

The helm chart template for the Pod Security Policy of the node collector was
missing the "emptyDir" volume and "CAP_SYS_PTRACE" capability it requires. These
have been added.
